reviews.text:
Very nice vape! Iam not the biggest fan of banana vapes , but this one i can enjoy. The Cream Milky Undertone mutes the Banana Cream down,&#xD;
that there is a very good balance between the Milk and the banana. Its good after 7 days, but it really shines at 10days+!&#xD;
For me it works better with 2.5% LB Vanilla Ice Cream. Its a little more than TPA VBIC, because its weaker. But this is a personal thing, the recipe is 5 stars, how it is.&#xD;
Thanks for the recipe Mr. G!&#xD;
PS.&#xD;
Made a Version where i replaced the GCC with FW Hazelnut at same amount and changed 1% of the VBIC with 1% TPA Vanilla Swirl.&#xD;
And i like that Version more, because its fuuler, and milkier and the Banana taste a little stronger.
